message: Added the precise dates of the Axis countries leaving the Axis, with Wiki links to how the leaving occurred. Italy announced its armistice on 8 September 1943, Bulgaria proclaimed its full neutrality on 17 august 1944 and Romania had its coup a few days later on the 23rd. Also added to Hungary a tag which mentions its status beginning with 15 March 1944 as a country under German occupation.
